<div id="acknowledgments">

<h3>Acknowledgments</h3>

<p>
Our sincere thanks to John Martin Fischer, Coleen Macnamara, Angela
Smith, and Gary Watson for all of their help thinking about moral
responsibility and blame over the years, and to the American Council
of Learned Societies and The College of William &amp; Mary for
financial assistance during the initial research for this entry.
Thanks also to Dee Payton and Patrick Todd for helpful discussions
about the issue of standing.</p>
